title: Duke Comes Up Short at Virginia Tech, 15-11 - Duke University - GoDuke.com
content: Duke Comes Up Short at Virginia Tech, 15-11 - Duke University  GoDuke.com
description: The Duke baseball team tallied 15 hits, including nine extra-base hits, but came up short in a slugfest against Virginia Tech, 15-11, at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
